WEBVTT

00:00:56.369 --> 00:01:01.382
are the great and fading
lessons of Apollo.

00:01:02.514 --> 00:01:06.545
And they are what give the word
"moonshot" its meaning.

00:01:07.498 --> 00:01:12.220
And our world is in desperate need
of political leaders

00:01:12.244 --> 00:01:16.029
willing to set bold deadlines

00:01:16.053 --> 00:01:19.981
for the achievement of daring dreams
on the scale of Apollo again.

00:01:22.368 --> 00:01:23.861
When I think about dreams,

00:01:23.885 --> 00:01:27.934
I think about the drag queens
of LA and Stonewall

00:01:27.958 --> 00:01:30.307
and millions of other people
risking everything